text: Soyuz MS-19 is a Soyuz spaceflight planned for launch on 5 October 2021. It will transport three members of the Expedition 67 crew to the International Space Station Soyuz MS-19 will be the 147th flight of a crewed Soyuz spacecraft. The crew will consist of a Russian commander and two Russian flight engineers. == Crew == === Backup crew === == References == Category:Crewed Soyuz missions Category:Future human spaceflights Category:2021 in spaceflight Category:2021 in Russia
